Phillip Van Dyke https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phillip_Van_Dyke 0 Phillip Van Dyke (born June 13, 1984) is a former American actor best known for his role as the goblin Luke in the first two installments of Disney's Halloweentown film series and Arnold in seasons two and three of Nickelodeon's Hey Arnold!.
